		</SENTENCE>
		<SENTENCE ID="3.3">
			<STRING>The fact that the headwaters of Río Apurímac are the source of the Amazon River was confirmed by Brazilian scientists in 2007, who pointed at Quebrada Apacheta as the most probable source of the Amazon. </STRING>
